    %h5 Your own wiki in seconds
    %p
      Get your own powerful, extensible, personal wiki in seconds with no installation
      required. Make it private or public.

  .col
    %h5 Powered by TiddlyWiki
    %p
      Tiddlyhost is powered by
      =link_to 'TiddlyWiki', 'https://tiddlywiki.com/'
      the revolutionary open source JavaScript wiki, created by
      =link_to('Jeremy Ruston', 'https://tiddlywiki.com/#JeremyRuston') + "."

  .col
